***[[榴槤|榴槤]]壳灰（DSA）：<ref>[https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S223878541930290X A novel preparation of visible light driven Durio zibethinus shell ash supported CuO nanocomposite for the photocatalytic degradation of acid dye]Science Direct，2019年11月15日</ref>
